Build ONLY the current phase. Do not jump ahead.

Roadmap:

- Phase 0: Project setup (done)
- Phase 1: Config & Omarchy theming
- Phase 2: Terminal core (Rust portable-pty backend + xterm.js WebGL frontend)
- Phase 3: Sidebar + sessions
- Phase 4: Splits & layout
- Phase 5: Notifications & glowing rings
- Phase 6: Browser pane (wry)
- Phase 7: Agent API (Unix socket + notify CLI)
- Phase 8: Polish & release (Hyprland rules, config, AUR)

After finishing a phase, reply only with "Phase X complete ✅" + list of changed/created files.
